 예외는 suppressed로 남아 주 예외를 잃지 않습니다. (",[27,748,240],{"href":238,"rel":749},[31],[35,751,752],{"id":752},"결론",[15,754,755],{},"자원 관리는 “해야 한다”가 아니라 **“실수할 수 없게 만들어야 한다”**에 가깝습니다.",[15,757,758,760,761,33],{},[23,759,5],{},"는 자원 해제를 기본 동작으로 고정하고, 예외가 겹쳐도 정보를 보존해 운영/디버깅 비용을 낮춥니다. (",[27,762,32],{"href":29,"rel":763},[31],[35,765,767],{"id":766},"참고공식-문서-링크","참고(공식 문서 링크)",[182,769,770,776,782,788,794],{},[185,771,772],{},[27,773,775],{"href":29,"rel":774},[31],"Oracle Java Tutorials — The try-with-resources Statement",[185,777,778],{},[27,779,781],{"href":51,"rel":780},[31],"Oracle API — AutoCloseable",[185,783,784],{},[27,785,787],{"href":238,"rel":786},[31],"Oracle API — Throwable (Suppressed 관련 메서드 포함)",[185,789,790],{},[27,791,793],{"href":224,"rel":792},[31],"Java Language Specification — try-with-resources 동작 규칙",[185,795,796],{},[27,797,800],{"href":798,"rel":799},"https://www.baeldung.com/java-suppressed-exceptions",[31],"Baeldung — Java Suppressed Exceptions",[802,803,804],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":100,"searchDepth":113,"depth":113,"links":806},[807,808,809,813,818,819,824,825,826],{"id":37,"depth":113,"text":38},{"id":63,"depth":113,"text":64},{"id":161,"depth":113,"text":162,"children":810},[811,812],{"id":166,"depth":119,"text":167},{"id":243,"depth":119,"text":244},{"id":289,"depth":113,"text":290,"children":814},[815,816,817],{"id":293,"depth":119,"text":294},{"id":343,"depth":119,"text":344},{"id":393,"depth":119,"text":394},{"id":588,"depth":113,"text":589},{"id":654,"depth":113,"text":655,"children":820}